###

# Update post
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/posts/a5b5eeb7-458a-4da4-b41b-cd977a575fe8 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": [
    "programming",
    "tutorial2"
  ],
  "status": "published",
  "repost": false,
  "authorId": "333",
  "type": "video",
  "title": "How to Build NestJS App2",
